sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import {Container, Row, Col} from 'react-bootstrap'; import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'; import {TestimonailSection, TestimonailsLayout, HeadingLayout, TestimonialHeading, TestimonialLayout, LeftQuote, TestimonialText, AuthorImageHolder, Img, TestimonialAuthor, AuthorDesignation } from './testimonials.style'; import { Testimonials } from '../../../pagedata/Home'; const OurStatsPage = () => { return( {Testimonials.TestimonialHeading} {Testimonials.TestimonialDetails[0].TestimonialText} {Testimonials.TestimonialDetails[0].TestimonialAuthor} {Testimonials.TestimonialDetails[0].AuthorDesignation} {Testimonials.TestimonialDetails[1].TestimonialText} {Testimonials.TestimonialDetails[1].TestimonialAuthor} {Testimonials.TestimonialDetails[1].AuthorDesignation} {Testimonials.TestimonialDetails[2].TestimonialText} {Testimonials.TestimonialDetails[2].TestimonialAuthor} {Testimonials.TestimonialDetails[2].AuthorDesignation} ); } export default OurStatsPage;
